export abstract class BorderRadius {
    static readonly none = 'rounded-none'
    static readonly sm = 'rounded-sm'
    static readonly rounded = 'rounded'
    static readonly md = 'rounded-md'
    static readonly lg = 'rounded-lg'
    static readonly xl = 'rounded-xl'
    static readonly _2xl = 'rounded-2xl'
    static readonly _3xl = 'rounded-3xl'
    static readonly full = 'rounded-full'
}
